{"id":"bcf44f53fe8c555f8640280d6d0edb6308204a5e","url":"https://www.pcjs.org/","title":"PCjs Machines","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"Lobsters (技术社区)","byline":"Unauthorized Windows 95","excerpt":"PCjs offers a variety of online machine emulators written in JavaScript. Run DOS, Windows, OS/2 and other vintage PC applications in a web browser on your desktop computer, iPhone, or iPad. An assortment of microcomputers, minicomputers, terminals, programmable calculators, and arcade machines are also available, along with an archive of historical software and documentation.","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section>\n        <h2 id=\"pcjs-heading\">Welcome to PCjs</h2>\n\n<p>PCjs uses JavaScript to emulate a small collection of hardware and software that I grew up with in the 1970s and 1980s,\nallowing you to experience their slow CPUs, low-resolution displays, and primitive sound effects, all in the comfort and\nsafety of your desktop or mobile web browser.</p>\n\n<p>Over time, PCjs emulations have expanded to include selected <a href=\"/machines/pcx86/compaq/deskpro386/\">IBM PC Compatibles</a>\nand more classic machines, such as <a href=\"/machines/dec/pdp11/\">Minicomputers</a>, <a href=\"/machines/ti/ti57/\">Programmable Calculators</a>,\n<a href=\"/machines/dec/vt100/\">Terminals</a>, and <a href=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/\">Arcade Games</a>.\nTo learn more or contribute to these very modest preservation efforts, visit the <a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar/pcjs\">PCjs</a>\nopen-source project on <a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"pcjs-highlights\">PCjs Highlights</h3>\n\n<p>Explore a variety of old PC public domain software and shareware.</p>\n\n<div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-magazines-pcdm\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcdm/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcdm/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC Disk Magazine (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>PC Disk Magazine <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-magazines-pcm\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcm/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcm/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC Magazine Utilities (1987)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>PC Magazine Utilities <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-misc-pcsig\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/misc/pcsig/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/misc/pcsig/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC-SIG Diskette Library (1990)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>PC-SIG Diskette Library <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n</div>\n<p>Interact with a variety of computer hardware and software from the past.  You can browse many more combinations, along with a small collection of related documentation, using the <a href=\"#pcjs-explorer\" onclick=\"pcjsExplorerView(this, event)\">PCjs Explorer</a>.</p>\n\n<div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-ti-ti57\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/ti/ti57/\"><img src=\"/machines/ti/ti57/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"TI-57 Programmable Calculator (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>TI-57 Programmable Calculator <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-osi-c1p\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/osi/c1p/\"><img src=\"/machines/osi/c1p/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-arcade-invaders\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/\"><img src=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Space Invaders (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Space Invaders <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-microsoft-adventure\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/microsoft/adventure/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/microsoft/adventure/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Adventure (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Adventure <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-ibm-basic-1-00-donkey\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/basic/1.00/donkey/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/basic/1.00/donkey/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-other-visicalc-1981\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/other/visicalc/1981/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/other/visicalc/1981/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"VisiCalc (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>VisiCalc <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-ibm-multiplan-1-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/multiplan/1.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/multiplan/1.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Multiplan 1.0 (1982)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Multiplan 1.0 <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1982-esuite\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1982/esuite/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1982/esuite/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Executive Suite (1982)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Executive Suite <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-dec-pdp11-1170-panel-debugger-rt11\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/dec/pdp11/1170/panel/debugger/rt11/\"><img src=\"/machines/dec/pdp11/1170/panel/debugger/rt11/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PDP-11/70 with RT-11 4.0 (1982)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>PDP-11/70 with RT-11 4.0 <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-cpm-1-1b\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/cpm/1.1b/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/cpm/1.1b/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"CP/M-86 (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>CP/M-86 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-pcx86-compaq-portable-vdu\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/pcx86/compaq/portable/vdu/\"><img src=\"/machines/pcx86/compaq/portable/vdu/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"COMPAQ Portable with Monochrome Graphics (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>COMPAQ Portable with Monochrome Graphics <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  \n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-demo-ibm-exploring-1-00-mda\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/demo/ibm/exploring/1.00-MDA/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/demo/ibm/exploring/1.00-MDA/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Exploring the IBM Personal Computer (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Exploring the IBM Personal Computer <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1983-adventmath\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1983/adventmath/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1983/adventmath/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Adventures in Math (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Adventures in Math <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-lotus-123-1a\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/lotus/123/1a/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/lotus/123/1a/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Lotus 1-2-3 (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Lotus 1-2-3 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-util-norton-2-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/util/norton/2.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/util/norton/2.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Norton Utilities 2.0 (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Norton Utilities 2.0 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-demo-ibm-ega\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/demo/ibm/ega/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/demo/ibm/ega/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Fantasy Land EGA Demo (1984)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Fantasy Land EGA Demo <br>(1984)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-microsoft-word-1-15\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/microsoft/word/1.15/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/microsoft/word/1.15/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Word 1.15 (1984)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Word 1.15 <br>(1984)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1985-nine-princes\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/nine_princes/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/nine_princes/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Nine Princes in Amber (1985)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Nine Princes in Amber <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1985-rogue\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/rogue/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/rogue/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Rogue (1985)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Rogue <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-1-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 1.0 (&quot;Premiere Edition&quot;)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.0 <br>(\"Premiere Edition\")</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-1-01-cga\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.01/cga/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.01/cga/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 1.1 on CGA (1985)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.1 on CGA <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-1-01-ega\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.01/ega/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/1.01/ega/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 1.1 on EGA (1985)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.1 on EGA <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1985-balance-of-power\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/balance_of_power/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1985/balance_of_power/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Balance of Power (1985)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Balance of Power <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-os2-ibm-1-0\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/os2/ibm/1.0/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/os2/ibm/1.0/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"IBM OS/2 1.0 (1987)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>IBM OS/2 1.0 <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-test-vga-blackbook\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/test/vga/blackbook/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/test/vga/blackbook/L23-1/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"VGA Black Book Tests (by Michael Abrash)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>VGA Black Book Tests <br>(by Michael Abrash)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-2-0x\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/2.0x/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/2.0x/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows/386 2.0 (1987)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows/386 2.0 <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-lang-microsoft-pascal-quickpascal-1-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/lang/microsoft/pascal/quickpascal/1.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/lang/microsoft/pascal/quickpascal/1.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft QuickPascal 1.00 (1989)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft QuickPascal 1.00 <br>(1989)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-3-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/3.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/3.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 3.0 (1990)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 3.0 <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1990-life-and-death-ii\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1990/life_and_death_ii/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1990/life_and_death_ii/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Life & Death II: The Brain (1990)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Life &amp; Death II: The Brain <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1991-oregon-trail\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1991/oregon_trail/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1991/oregon_trail/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"The Oregon Trail (1991)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>The Oregon Trail <br>(1991)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-id-commander-keen\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/id/commander_keen/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/id/commander_keen/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Commander Keen (1991)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Commander Keen <br>(1991)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-id-wolf3d\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/id/wolf3d/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/id/wolf3d/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Wolfenstein 3D (1992)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Wolfenstein 3D <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1992-dune2\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1992/dune2/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1992/dune2/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Dune II (1992)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Dune II <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-3-10\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/3.10/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/3.10/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 3.1 (1992)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 3.1 <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sys-windows-win95-4-00-950\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/win95/4.00.950/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sys/windows/win95/4.00.950/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Windows 95 (1995)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p><span>Microsoft Windows 95 <br>(1995)</span>\n  </p></div>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>Thanks for visiting!<br>\n–<a href=\"mailto:Jeff@pcjs.org\">Jeff</a></p>\n\n\n<p>[<a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar/pcjs/tree/gh-pages/\">GitHub Source</a>]</p>\n      </section></DIV>","content_text":"Welcome to PCjs PCjs uses JavaScript to emulate a small collection of hardware and software that I grew up with in the 1970s and 1980s, allowing you to experience their slow CPUs, low-resolution displays, and primitive sound effects, all in the comfort and safety of your desktop or mobile web browser. Over time, PCjs emulations have expanded to include selected IBM PC Compatibles and more classic machines, such as Minicomputers, Programmable Calculators, Terminals, and Arcade Games. To learn more or contribute to these very modest preservation efforts, visit the PCjs open-source project on GitHub. PCjs Highlights Explore a variety of old PC public domain software and shareware. PC Disk Magazine (1983) PC Magazine Utilities (1987) PC-SIG Diskette Library (1990) Interact with a variety of computer hardware and software from the past. You can browse many more combinations, along with a small collection of related documentation, using the PCjs Explorer. TI-57 Programmable Calculator (1978) Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P (1978) Space Invaders (1978) Microsoft Adventure (1981) DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 (1981) VisiCalc (1981) Multiplan 1.0 (1982) Executive Suite (1982) PDP-11/70 with RT-11 4.0 (1982) CP/M-86 (1983) COMPAQ Portable with Monochrome Graphics (1983) Exploring the IBM Personal Computer (1983) Adventures in Math (1983) Lotus 1-2-3 (1983) Norton Utilities 2.0 (1983) Fantasy Land EGA Demo (1984) Microsoft Word 1.15 (1984) Nine Princes in Amber (1985) Rogue (1985) Microsoft Windows 1.0 (\"Premiere Edition\") Microsoft Windows 1.1 on CGA (1985) Microsoft Windows 1.1 on EGA (1985) Balance of Power (1985) IBM OS/2 1.0 (1987) VGA Black Book Tests (by Michael Abrash) Microsoft Windows/386 2.0 (1987) Microsoft QuickPascal 1.00 (1989) Microsoft Windows 3.0 (1990) Life & Death II: The Brain (1990) The Oregon Trail (1991) Commander Keen (1991) Wolfenstein 3D (1992) Dune II (1992) Microsoft Windows 3.1 (1992) Microsoft Windows 95 (1995) Thanks for visiting! –Jeff [GitHub Source]","fetched_at":"2026-07-23T08:58:19.702Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<h2 id=\"pcjs-heading\">Welcome to PCjs</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Welcome to PCjs","zh":"欢迎来到PCjs"}]},{"html_en":"<p>PCjs uses JavaScript to emulate a small collection of hardware and software that I grew up with in the 1970s and 1980s,\nallowing you to experience their slow CPUs, low-resolution displays, and primitive sound effects, all in the comfort and\nsafety of your desktop or mobile web browser.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"PCjs uses JavaScript to emulate a small collection of hardware and software that I grew up with in the 1970s and 1980s, allowing you to experience their slow CPUs, low-resolution displays, and primitive sound effects, all in the comfort and safety of your desktop or mobile web browser.","zh":"PCjs 使用 JavaScript 来模拟我在 20 世纪 70 年代和 1980 年代长大的一小部分硬件和软件，让您可以在桌面或移动 Web 浏览器中舒适、安全地体验它们的缓慢 CPU、低分辨率显示器和原始音效。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Over time, PCjs emulations have expanded to include selected <a href=\"/machines/pcx86/compaq/deskpro386/\">IBM PC Compatibles</a>\nand more classic machines, such as <a href=\"/machines/dec/pdp11/\">Minicomputers</a>, <a href=\"/machines/ti/ti57/\">Programmable Calculators</a>,\n<a href=\"/machines/dec/vt100/\">Terminals</a>, and <a href=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/\">Arcade Games</a>.\nTo learn more or contribute to these very modest preservation efforts, visit the <a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar/pcjs\">PCjs</a>\nopen-source project on <a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar\">GitHub</a>.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Over time, PCjs emulations have expanded to include selected IBM PC Compatibles and more classic machines, such as Minicomputers, Programmable Calculators, Terminals, and Arcade Games.","zh":"随着时间的推移，PCjs 仿真已经扩展到包括选定的 IBM PC 兼容机和更多经典机器，例如小型计算机、可编程计算器、终端和街机游戏。"},{"en":"To learn more or contribute to these very modest preservation efforts, visit the PCjs open-source project on GitHub.","zh":"要了解更多信息或为这些非常有限的保护工作做出贡献，请访问 GitHub 上的 PCjs 开源项目。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3 id=\"pcjs-highlights\">PCjs Highlights</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"PCjs Highlights","zh":"PCjs 亮点"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Explore a variety of old PC public domain software and shareware.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Explore a variety of old PC public domain software and shareware.","zh":"探索各种旧的 PC 公共领域软件和共享软件。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>PC Disk Magazine <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"PC Disk Magazine (1983)","zh":"PC 磁盘杂志 (1983)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>PC Magazine Utilities <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"PC Magazine Utilities (1987)","zh":"PC 杂志实用程序 (1987)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>PC-SIG Diskette Library <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"PC-SIG Diskette Library (1990)","zh":"PC-SIG 软盘库 (1990)"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Interact with a variety of computer hardware and software from the past.  You can browse many more combinations, along with a small collection of related documentation, using the <a href=\"#pcjs-explorer\" onclick=\"pcjsExplorerView(this, event)\">PCjs Explorer</a>.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Interact with a variety of computer hardware and software from the past.","zh":"与过去的各种计算机硬件和软件进行交互。"},{"en":"You can browse many more combinations, along with a small collection of related documentation, using the PCjs Explorer.","zh":"您可以使用 PCjs Explorer 浏览更多组合以及一小部分相关文档。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>TI-57 Programmable Calculator <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"TI-57 Programmable Calculator (1978)","zh":"TI-57 可编程计算器 (1978)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P (1978)","zh":"俄亥俄州科学挑战者 1P (1978)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Space Invaders <br>(1978)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Space Invaders (1978)","zh":"太空侵略者 (1978)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Adventure <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Adventure (1981)","zh":"微软冒险 (1981)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 (1981)","zh":"PC DOS 1.00 (1981) 中的 DONKEY.BAS"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>VisiCalc <br>(1981)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"VisiCalc (1981)","zh":"可视计算器 (1981)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Multiplan 1.0 <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Multiplan 1.0 (1982)","zh":"多重计划 1.0 (1982)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Executive Suite <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Executive Suite (1982)","zh":"行政套房（1982）"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>PDP-11/70 with RT-11 4.0 <br>(1982)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"PDP-11/70 with RT-11 4.0 (1982)","zh":"PDP-11/70 与 RT-11 4.0 (1982)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>CP/M-86 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p><span>COMPAQ Portable with Monochrome Graphics <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"COMPAQ Portable with Monochrome Graphics (1983)","zh":"康柏便携式单色显卡 (1983)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Exploring the IBM Personal Computer <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Exploring the IBM Personal Computer (1983)","zh":"探索 IBM 个人计算机 (1983)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Adventures in Math <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Adventures in Math (1983)","zh":"数学历险记 (1983)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Lotus 1-2-3 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Norton Utilities 2.0 <br>(1983)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Norton Utilities 2.0 (1983)","zh":"诺顿实用工具 2.0 (1983)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Fantasy Land EGA Demo <br>(1984)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Fantasy Land EGA Demo (1984)","zh":"幻想之地 EGA 演示 (1984)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Word 1.15 <br>(1984)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Word 1.15 (1984)","zh":"微软Word 1.15 (1984)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Nine Princes in Amber <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Nine Princes in Amber (1985)","zh":"琥珀九王子 (1985)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Rogue <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.0 <br>(\"Premiere Edition\")</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 1.0 (\"Premiere Edition\")","zh":"Microsoft Windows 1.0（“首映版”）"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.1 on CGA <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 1.1 on CGA (1985)","zh":"CGA 上的 Microsoft Windows 1.1 (1985)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 1.1 on EGA <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 1.1 on EGA (1985)","zh":"EGA 上的 Microsoft Windows 1.1 (1985)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Balance of Power <br>(1985)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Balance of Power (1985)","zh":"权力平衡 (1985)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>IBM OS/2 1.0 <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p><span>VGA Black Book Tests <br>(by Michael Abrash)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"VGA Black Book Tests (by Michael Abrash)","zh":"VGA 黑皮书测试（Michael Abrash）"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows/386 2.0 <br>(1987)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows/386 2.0 (1987)","zh":"微软 Windows/386 2.0 (1987)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft QuickPascal 1.00 <br>(1989)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft QuickPascal 1.00 (1989)","zh":"微软 QuickPascal 1.00 (1989)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 3.0 <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 3.0 (1990)","zh":"微软视窗 3.0 (1990)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Life &amp; Death II: The Brain <br>(1990)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Life & Death II: The Brain (1990)","zh":"生与死 II：大脑 (1990)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>The Oregon Trail <br>(1991)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"The Oregon Trail (1991)","zh":"俄勒冈小道 (1991)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Commander Keen <br>(1991)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Commander Keen (1991)","zh":"基恩指挥官 (1991)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Wolfenstein 3D <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Wolfenstein 3D (1992)","zh":"德军总部 3D (1992)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Dune II <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Dune II (1992)","zh":"沙丘 II (1992)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 3.1 <br>(1992)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 3.1 (1992)","zh":"微软视窗 3.1 (1992)"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Microsoft Windows 95 <br>(1995)</span>\n  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Microsoft Windows 95 (1995)","zh":"微软视窗 95 (1995)"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Thanks for visiting!<br>\n–<a href=\"mailto:Jeff@pcjs.org\">Jeff</a></p>","sentences":[{"en":"Thanks for visiting! –Jeff","zh":"感谢您的光临！ ——杰夫"}]},{"html_en":"<p>[<a href=\"https://github.com/jeffpar/pcjs/tree/gh-pages/\">GitHub Source</a>]</p>","sentences":[{"en":"[GitHub Source]","zh":"[GitHub 来源]"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section>\n        <h2 id=\"pcjs-heading\">欢迎来到PCjs</h2>\n\n<p>PCjs 使用 JavaScript 来模拟我在 20 世纪 70 年代和 1980 年代长大的一小部分硬件和软件，让您可以在桌面或移动 Web 浏览器中舒适、安全地体验它们的缓慢 CPU、低分辨率显示器和原始音效。</p>\n\n<p>随着时间的推移，PCjs 仿真已经扩展到包括选定的 IBM PC 兼容机和更多经典机器，例如小型计算机、可编程计算器、终端和街机游戏。 要了解更多信息或为这些非常有限的保护工作做出贡献，请访问 GitHub 上的 PCjs 开源项目。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"pcjs-highlights\">PCjs 亮点</h3>\n\n<p>探索各种旧的 PC 公共领域软件和共享软件。</p>\n\n<div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-magazines-pcdm\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcdm/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcdm/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC Disk Magazine (1983)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>PC 磁盘杂志 (1983)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-magazines-pcm\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcm/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/magazines/pcm/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC Magazine Utilities (1987)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>PC 杂志实用程序 (1987)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-sw-misc-pcsig\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/sw/misc/pcsig/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/sw/misc/pcsig/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"PC-SIG Diskette Library (1990)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>PC-SIG 软盘库 (1990)</p></div>\n\n</div>\n<p>与过去的各种计算机硬件和软件进行交互。 您可以使用 PCjs Explorer 浏览更多组合以及一小部分相关文档。</p>\n\n<div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-ti-ti57\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/ti/ti57/\"><img src=\"/machines/ti/ti57/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"TI-57 Programmable Calculator (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>TI-57 可编程计算器 (1978)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-osi-c1p\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/osi/c1p/\"><img src=\"/machines/osi/c1p/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Ohio Scientific Challenger 1P (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>俄亥俄州科学挑战者 1P (1978)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-machines-arcade-invaders\">\n    <p><a href=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/\"><img src=\"/machines/arcade/invaders/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Space Invaders (1978)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>太空侵略者 (1978)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-microsoft-adventure\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/microsoft/adventure/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/game/microsoft/adventure/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Microsoft Adventure (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>微软冒险 (1981)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-ibm-basic-1-00-donkey\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/basic/1.00/donkey/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/basic/1.00/donkey/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"DONKEY.BAS from PC DOS 1.00 (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>PC DOS 1.00 (1981) 中的 DONKEY.BAS</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-other-visicalc-1981\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/other/visicalc/1981/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/other/visicalc/1981/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"VisiCalc (1981)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>可视计算器 (1981)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-app-ibm-multiplan-1-00\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/multiplan/1.00/\"><img src=\"/software/pcx86/app/ibm/multiplan/1.00/images/thumbnail.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"128\" alt=\"Multiplan 1.0 (1982)\" title=\"\"></a>\n    </p>\n    <p>多重计划 1.0 (1982)</p></div>\n\n  <div id=\"featured-software-pcx86-game-other-1982-esuite\">\n    <p><a href=\"/software/pcx86/game/other/1982/esuite/\"><img src=\"/software